The '''Brimstone chest''' can be found next to [[Konar quo Maten]] on [[Mount Karuulm]]. The chest is locked and can only be opened by using a [[brimstone key]], which is obtained from killing monsters that Konar assigns the player.

The exact odds of receiving the key are 1/100 for level 100 monsters and 1/50 for level 350 monsters, scaling linearly and capping at 350 as shown in formula 2.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Kieren|url=https://twitter.com/JagexKieren/status/1083781544135847936|date=16 January 2019|archiveurl=https://archive.is/g6A5h|archivedate=26 May 2020|quote=It follows a curve up until level 100 then scales linearly between those 2 values upto level 350 combat. Creatures over thsi{{sic}} will cap at 1/50. [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DwpdLK2W0AEynZy.jpg]}} For lower level monsters, it follows a curve: as shown in formula 1.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Kieren|url=https://twitter.com/JagexKieren/status/1083783815141707781|date=16 January 2019|archiveurl=https://archive.is/G2QQq|archivedate=29 April 2020|quote=0.2*(CBLEVEL - 100)^2 + 100}}

<math>\begin{align}
P(L) &= \frac{1}{100 + \lfloor (100 - L)^2/5 \rfloor} & L \in (0, 100) && (1) \\
P(L) &= \frac{1}{120 - \lfloor L/5 \rfloor} & L \in [100, 350] && (2)
\end{align}</math>

<math>
\text{Where P is the probability of a drop and L is the monster's combat level.}
</math>

==Possible loot==
{{DropLogProject|jagex=yes}}

The brimstone chest usually contains generic loot meant as a slight increase to the player's profits. There is also a rare chance of getting a [[broken dragon hasta]], which can be repaired, for free, by simply showing it to [[Otto Godblessed]] ([[Barbarian Training]] in [[Smithing]] is '''not''' required for this). There's also a slim chance of obtaining pieces of the dusk [[mystic robes|mystic robe set]], which come with a colour scheme similar to that of [[Mount Karuulm]].

The average value of a drop from this table is {{Coins|{{KDTValue}}}}.{{CiteDevBlog|url=https://services.runescape.com/m=news/revised-post-kebos-poll-blog?oldschool=1|author=The Old School Team|blogdate=21 January 2019|accessdate=21 January 2019|title=Revised Post Kebos Poll Blog}}

